### Create a build

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/builds" \
  -X POST \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]" \
  -H "Content-type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "lifecycle": {
      "type": "buildpack",
      "data": {
        "buildpacks": ["http://github.example.org/myorg/awesome-buildpack"],
        "stack": "cflinuxfs2"
      }
    },
    "package": {
       "guid": "[package-guid]"
    }
  }'
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 201 Created
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_staging_build %>
```

